{"title":"Knog Scout Bike Alarm Connects to iOS","link":"https://theradavist.com/knog-scout-bike-alarm/","date":1716407022000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1620\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Scout_Bike_Hero_web_1340x.jpg?fit=1200,1080&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Scout_Bike_Hero_web_1340x.jpg?w=1620&amp;quality=75 1620w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Scout_Bike_Hero_web_1340x.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Scout_Bike_Hero_web_1340x.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/Scout_Bike_Hero_web_1340x.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em>In an era where no bike is safe in cities, Knog just announced its all-new <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=b7c689ca-2b68-4129-8c2d-4beda666c19d&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fus.knog.com%2Fproducts%2Fscout\" target=\"_blank\">Scout</a> ($59.95), a motion-sensitive audio and iOS bike alarm device that fits under a bottle cage…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/knog_scout_bike_12998_lifestyle_2.jpg?fit=1200,1280&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/knog_scout_bike_12998_lifestyle_2.jpg?w=1920&amp;quality=75 1920w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/knog_scout_bike_12998_lifestyle_2.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/knog_scout_bike_12998_lifestyle_2.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/knog_scout_bike_12998_lifestyle_2.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/knog_scout_bike_12998_lifestyle_7.jpg?fit=1200,1280&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/knog_scout_bike_12998_lifestyle_7.jpg?w=1920&amp;quality=75 1920w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/knog_scout_bike_12998_lifestyle_7.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/knog_scout_bike_12998_lifestyle_7.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/knog_scout_bike_12998_lifestyle_7.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/knog_scout_bike_12998_lifestyle_6.jpg?fit=1200,1280&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/knog_scout_bike_12998_lifestyle_6.jpg?w=1920&amp;quality=75 1920w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/knog_scout_bike_12998_lifestyle_6.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/knog_scout_bike_12998_lifestyle_6.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/knog_scout_bike_12998_lifestyle_6.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Once armed, any movement of a Scout-fitted bike will trigger the motion-sensitive audio alarm, discouraging further movement and alerting the bike’s owner, both by the sound of the alarm and via a notification automatically sent to the owner’s iPhone (when in Bluetooth range).</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2867\" height=\"1612\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/KnogScout.jpg?fit=1200,1612&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/KnogScout.jpg?w=2867&amp;quality=75 2867w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/KnogScout.jpg?resize=1200,675&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/KnogScout.jpg?resize=2000,1125&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/KnogScout.jpg?resize=768,432&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/KnogScout.jpg?resize=1536,864&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/05/KnogScout.jpg?resize=2048,1152&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Then, in a scenario where a bike fitted with the Scout is not where the owner has left it, it can be quickly located using Apple’s ‘Find My’ app.</p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatible with iOS only</li>\n<li>Motion-sensitive 85 db audio alarm for immediate deterrence</li>\n<li>Can be located quickly using Apple’s ‘Find My’ app</li>\n<li>Operated using Knog’s iOS app</li>\n<li>Mounts to standard water cage braze-ons</li>\n<li>Can be mounted underwater cage for discretion</li>\n<li>Use supplied anti-tamper screws to mount securely</li>\n<li>Arm / disarm using a button (within 1.5 m) or app within Bluetooth range</li>\n<li>LEDs show alarm status &amp; battery charge</li>\n<li>USB-C rechargeable with 2 to 6 month battery (pending usage)</li>\n<li>Low battery notifications when you have just 20% remaining</li>\n<li>Water-resistant IP66 rating (wash-proof)</li>\n<li>Weighs just 25 grams</li>\n<li>USB-C charging cable not included</li>\n<li>Run Time – Up to 6 months. Expect around 2 months if arming daily.</li>\n<li>Charge Time – 4 hours</li>\n<li>Dimensions – 10.7 x 2.5 x 0.8 cm / 4.2 x 1.0 x 0.3 in</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=b7c689ca-2b68-4129-8c2d-4beda666c19d&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fus.knog.com%2Fproducts%2Fscout\" target=\"_blank\">Knog</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/knog-scout-bike-alarm/\">Knog Scout Bike Alarm Connects to iOS</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"72b53e298a67f94e00eb1fa56687266bd791675b8efd510882320cfa821d88e7","category":"Cycling"}